{"tid":1507282,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我地要為popo正名 為真正核彈都唔切鋪路","createTime":"2019-08-26T05:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T07:21:10.000Z","uid":34047,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f0fc6a3bd9f03a05d5a04c6d0a6d95c0c76ca5b3","tid":1507282,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"叫佢地黑社會的確係好貼切<br />\n但如果我地既行動要再進一步<br />\n就要為佢地附上一個更具體既名<br />\n等大家 包括中立同淺黃<br />\n知我地對抗緊既係乜野人<br />\n真正令佢地核彈都唔切<br />\n<br />\n大家可以提議下<br />\n其中暫時諗到既<br />\n1. 種族滅絕部隊<br />\n(提醒大家我地對抗既係種族滅絕)<br />\n2. 港共兵團<br />\n3. 香港軍閥兵團 (參考陳雲)<br />\n<br />\n呢個名一定要叫到街知巷聞<br />\n甚至連媒體都要用<br />\n大家先會將佢地邪惡形象入腦<br />\n到時出核彈都冇人再覺得有問題<br />\n就算錯手有敵方死左<br />\n香港人只會覺得我地係做緊正義既事"},{"pid":"f2209ac2d258a0afa2be2e7e497e151a8715e953","tid":1507282,"uid":29899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:43:03.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1．13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=17788aa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文文宣建議：</strong></span><br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04wmZVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04wmZVM.jpg&h=efdc3dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06bd9a16f06508a9537cf8024148422c2ccc4606","tid":1507282,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:43:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=bc297c95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"865e202c26cd8f8fec3ef732da5ecab54388d9f3","tid":1507282,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f066fe9031952796e047cad458d77edc948320b5","tid":1507282,"uid":60658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:44:35.000Z","msg":"黨衛軍"}